  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>背景介绍：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tHappiness is thought of as the good life, freedom from suffering, flourishing, well-being, joy, prosperity, and pleasure.</p>\n<p>\n\tResearchers have formed a useful framework for studying happiness:<br />\n\t&bull; Happiness is made up of pleasure, engagement, and meaning<br />\n\t&bull; It involves both daily positive emotions and a global sense that life is worthwhile<br />\n\t&bull; People can accurately report their own levels of happiness</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWhat do we really know about happiness?<br />\n\tCan we study it?<br />\n\tAre we born with it?<br />\n\tCan we make ourselves happier?<br />\n\tWho&rsquo;s happy and who&rsquo;s not, and why?<br />\n\tWhat makes us happy?<br />\n\tetc....</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\tHappiness is inside you.</p>\n<p>\n\tI'm happy smelling the cold air and the burning wood in the winter evenings, watching the sea, listening to good music, I'm happy spending my time with my affairs, being useful, making people smile, I'm happy. There is no standard recipe. What makes me happy not <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/necessarily\" target=\"_blank\">necessarily</a> makes you happy either. The only way to be so is to comprehend yourself by accepting your deepest needs, emotions, thoughts and sensibilities. Quite often we are unable to reach happiness, just because we are unable to forgive our own mistakes, though who's been damaged of them maybe already has. Errors are important, once you are in the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/condition\" target=\"_blank\">condition</a> to recognise and accept them of being so, they help you become a better person. To reach happiness demands <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/interior\" target=\"_blank\">interior</a> <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/serenity\" target=\"_blank\">serenity</a>. Get to know yourself better, then everything comes easier.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例2：</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\tTo Be Simple and To Be Happy</p>\n<p>\n\tWhat is happiness in your eyes? You may have different answers. If I reply to this question, the answer will be quite simple.<br />\n\tHappiness is not to dream what you can possess but to enjoy what you have gotten. Happiness doesn't mean what achievements you have made or can make but that you can have a sense of obtaining much more just from the simple and small things that you have done. Happiness will not necessarily demand that you have a large house, but a warm home on the contrary. Just as the word home means not the same as house does, so does happiness and being happy. I prefer to think that retaining happiness is one man's life goal while keeping being happy is nothing but a short-term aim or <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/temporary\" target=\"_blank\">temporary</a> state of life.<br />\n\tAnd I would not like to write too much more because the true meaning of happiness and happiness itself is so simple, that is to live simple.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到主持人专业的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/item/767793/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p488566/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p488566\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p489057/\">毛腿防狼丝袜网络走红 口味太重你敢穿出去吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p489053/\">猫咪的秘密生活：你不在家时猫咪都在做什么？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p488960/\">热门TED演讲：二十岁是不是可以挥霍的光阴？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p427945/\">从零基础到英语达人：新概念帮你轻松搞定！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p488890/\">爱喝红茶吗？关于红茶你可能不知道的11大益处</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p487211/\">2013暑期雅思单项突围计划-大学篇</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p489051/\">爆笑HR语录：混外企千万别惹HR</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p489247/\">迪拜公主塔电梯故障 富豪要爬97层楼回家</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p489113/\">傲娇的英国人：那些不交电视费的奇葩理由</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p482910/\">谁说我不懂PPT：10课时从PPT新手到高手</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
